WEBVTT

01:42.840 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

02:24.840 --> 02:25.680
What's wrong?

02:27.600 --> 02:29.240
What are you doing, Duan Jiaxu?

02:29.320 --> 02:30.360
What did you call me?

02:31.120 --> 02:33.240
I mean, what did you just do?

02:33.320 --> 02:35.160
Given our current relationship,

02:35.240 --> 02:37.120
you shouldn't be calling me Duan Jiaxu.

02:37.200 --> 02:38.680
You…

02:38.760 --> 02:40.320
I wasn't asleep just now.

02:40.400 --> 02:41.680
I knew what you were doing.

02:43.600 --> 02:45.240
So you weren't asleep, were you?

02:45.760 --> 02:47.160
What did I do just now then?

02:49.920 --> 02:50.800
Tell me.

02:57.200 --> 02:59.320
Come closer. I won't say it out loud.

03:02.080 --> 03:03.240
Closer.

03:04.960 --> 03:06.400
Do you want to whisper it?

03:15.440 --> 03:16.400
I don't know

03:17.120 --> 03:18.520
what I've done either.

03:24.720 --> 03:26.280
That was unexpected.

03:30.080 --> 03:33.320
Even though I did that just now,

03:33.400 --> 03:34.600
it doesn't mean

03:35.720 --> 03:37.640
that I have feelings for you.

03:37.720 --> 03:39.680
Got it? I mean…

03:39.760 --> 03:41.120
I haven't agreed yet.

03:41.800 --> 03:44.160
It doesn't mean you have feelings for me.

03:45.160 --> 03:47.000
That means you took advantage of me.

03:50.280 --> 03:52.800
Well, you took advantage of me first.

03:54.560 --> 03:56.640
Are you saying

03:57.200 --> 03:58.760
that no matter what I do to you,

03:58.840 --> 04:00.040
you will do the same to me?

04:01.240 --> 04:02.520
That's not what I meant.

04:04.840 --> 04:06.360
If you do this again,

04:06.440 --> 04:07.840
I will tell my brother.

04:07.920 --> 04:08.800
Go ahead.

04:09.440 --> 04:10.480
Tell him.

04:12.320 --> 04:13.760
After all,

04:13.840 --> 04:16.079
we'll have to go public sooner or later.

04:16.160 --> 04:17.720
It's better to do it sooner.

04:26.240 --> 04:28.080
I haven't agreed yet.

04:30.440 --> 04:32.080
I've successfully brainwashed you.

04:35.520 --> 04:36.600
Jiaxu…

04:38.000 --> 04:39.240
Stop looking at me.

04:43.840 --> 04:46.360
Jiaxu, you should leave.

04:46.440 --> 04:47.920
I can't focus if you stay here.

04:49.720 --> 04:51.480
Hi, everyone.

04:52.080 --> 04:53.280
- Hello.
- Hello.

04:53.360 --> 04:54.200
I'm an alumnus.

04:54.280 --> 04:55.760
- I'm Wang Lin.
- The speaker is here.

04:55.840 --> 04:58.160
The topic of today's sharing session

04:58.240 --> 04:59.400
is future career planning.

05:00.360 --> 05:01.280
Nice!

05:05.320 --> 05:07.840
I know it seems early to talk about this

05:07.920 --> 05:09.200
since you are only freshmen.

05:09.280 --> 05:12.040
However, I believe in being prepared.

05:15.320 --> 05:16.240
Left.

05:16.320 --> 05:17.760
To the left. That's right.

05:20.520 --> 05:21.360
What's wrong?

05:21.440 --> 05:22.320
Yu Xin, look!

05:22.840 --> 05:23.760
What is it?

05:23.840 --> 05:26.080
Sangsang's crush attended her class!

05:26.160 --> 05:27.520
- Look.
- Seriously?

05:27.600 --> 05:28.440
Yes.

05:30.040 --> 05:31.560
They attract so much attention.

05:32.320 --> 05:33.640
- I like it.
- I bet I know why.

05:33.720 --> 05:35.240
He bailed on Sangsang several times,

05:35.320 --> 05:37.240
so he specifically came

05:37.320 --> 05:38.200
to make it up to her!

05:52.880 --> 05:55.120
It feels nice to walk around

05:55.640 --> 05:56.680
on campus.

05:58.720 --> 05:59.680
Didn't you take walks

05:59.760 --> 06:01.160
during your time at university?

06:01.720 --> 06:02.680
I didn't.

06:03.360 --> 06:05.080
Why would I? I had no one to walk with.

06:05.160 --> 06:06.920
Didn't my brother take walks with you?

06:07.400 --> 06:09.120
Your brother taking walks with me?

06:10.400 --> 06:11.800
Am I that desperate?

06:12.440 --> 06:13.560
I'll tell him you said that.

06:15.960 --> 06:17.840
If you enjoy taking walks,

06:18.400 --> 06:20.760
I can keep you company today.

06:21.320 --> 06:23.000
Chen Qiang, go for it!

06:23.080 --> 06:24.920
Chen Qiang, you've got this!

06:25.000 --> 06:27.080
You are the best, Chen Qiang!

06:27.160 --> 06:28.680
- It's Weiwei.
- Chen Qiang, go!

06:28.760 --> 06:29.680
- Want to watch?
- Enough.

06:29.760 --> 06:32.840
- Sure. Let's go.
- Everyone knows he's your boyfriend.

06:34.360 --> 06:35.360
Go for it!

06:35.440 --> 06:37.440
Chen Qiang, go for it!

06:37.520 --> 06:39.120
- You startled me.
- You guys are here too.

06:39.200 --> 06:40.200
- Hi.
- Hi, guys.

06:40.280 --> 06:41.760
- Hello.
- Are you here to watch the game too?

06:42.440 --> 06:44.240
He said he wanted to watch.

06:44.320 --> 06:45.160
Look at Chen Qiang.

06:50.040 --> 06:50.960
Is that your boyfriend?

06:51.040 --> 06:51.920
Yes.

06:52.440 --> 06:53.320
Isn't he cool?

06:57.760 --> 06:59.560
- Are you okay?
- Are you okay?

06:59.640 --> 07:01.440
- Are you okay, Jiang Ming?
- Jiang Ming!

07:01.520 --> 07:02.680
Can you still play?

07:02.760 --> 07:03.880
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine.

07:03.960 --> 07:04.960
I'm okay.

07:05.040 --> 07:06.080
Are you hurt?

07:06.720 --> 07:08.360
- Are you okay?
- Did you sprain your ankle?

07:09.080 --> 07:10.000
Yes.

07:10.080 --> 07:11.520
Elevate your foot.

07:11.600 --> 07:13.120
- Use this iced tea.
- Apply it here.

07:13.600 --> 07:14.560
Thank you.

07:16.080 --> 07:17.360
You should go to the infirmary.

07:17.920 --> 07:18.840
It's okay.

07:18.920 --> 07:19.880
This is an old injury.

07:19.960 --> 07:21.360
I'll be better after resting.

07:21.440 --> 07:23.080
Now we're down one player.

07:23.160 --> 07:24.680
Why don't you guys

07:24.760 --> 07:25.920
find someone to replace me?

07:28.320 --> 07:29.520
Hey.

07:30.120 --> 07:31.200
Can you fill in?

07:33.400 --> 07:34.240
Can I?

07:36.080 --> 07:37.040
Can you play?

07:39.600 --> 07:40.920
Come on. Let's play.

07:41.000 --> 07:41.880
Let's go.

07:42.560 --> 07:43.400
Get some rest.

07:43.480 --> 07:44.520
Hold this for me.

07:47.280 --> 07:48.160
Wait here for me.

07:49.640 --> 07:50.640
You will defend him.

07:57.080 --> 07:58.240
He's pretty good.

08:01.640 --> 08:03.400
Hey! Nice shot!

08:03.480 --> 08:05.760
Sangsang, your crush is pretty good.

08:05.840 --> 08:07.480
That's not just pretty good, okay?

08:07.560 --> 08:09.520
He's perfect.

08:09.600 --> 08:11.920
Sangsang is being pursued
by such a perfect guy.

08:12.000 --> 08:13.120
She's so lucky.

08:15.400 --> 08:17.040
Good job!

08:17.120 --> 08:18.200
Good job!

08:18.280 --> 08:19.560
Nice game!

08:19.640 --> 08:20.600
Shoot!

08:21.640 --> 08:22.480
Come.

08:23.160 --> 08:24.120
Okay.

08:28.760 --> 08:29.720
Yes! Nice job!

08:29.800 --> 08:31.040
He's really good!

08:31.120 --> 08:32.480
- Nice!
- Impressive!

08:38.880 --> 08:40.120
It went in!

08:51.200 --> 08:52.760
He's quite good.

08:53.800 --> 08:55.880
Isn't that guy Sang Zhi's brother?

08:56.600 --> 08:57.880
You misunderstood.

08:57.960 --> 08:59.600
They aren't related.

09:07.680 --> 09:09.760
Have some iced tea after the game.

09:09.840 --> 09:10.680
Thank you.

09:11.280 --> 09:12.600
- Here.
- Do you need a drink?

09:27.000 --> 09:29.280
CHAPTER 17, FALLEN

09:29.360 --> 09:31.320
I WANT US TO BE TOGETHER

09:34.200 --> 09:35.440
Girls.

09:35.520 --> 09:37.480
Do you have any summer plans?

09:37.560 --> 09:39.600
Are you going home or traveling?

09:40.960 --> 09:42.320
I'm not going home for the break.

09:43.160 --> 09:44.280
No?

09:44.360 --> 09:45.480
Where are you going then?

09:45.560 --> 09:46.920
Chen Qiang and I have made plans.

09:47.000 --> 09:48.880
We are going to travel

09:48.960 --> 09:50.400
during the summer break.

09:50.480 --> 09:51.760
Really?

09:52.320 --> 09:53.600
That's so romantic.

09:53.680 --> 09:56.560
- How nice.
- I previously made a game prototype.

09:56.640 --> 09:58.960
A design company has shown interest.

09:59.040 --> 10:00.240
I'm going to intern

10:00.320 --> 10:01.880
at their company this summer.

10:02.600 --> 10:04.920
- Really?
- Congratulations.

10:05.920 --> 10:07.400
Interning during freshman year?

10:07.480 --> 10:08.440
That's right!

10:08.960 --> 10:10.120
It's a great company.

10:10.200 --> 10:12.200
I have to seize the opportunity.

10:12.280 --> 10:14.800
Sangsang, are you going home
for the summer?

10:15.360 --> 10:16.320
I…

10:17.320 --> 10:19.040
Or are you staying here with your crush?

10:21.720 --> 10:23.000
He's too busy.

10:23.080 --> 10:24.960
I don't think he has time for me.

10:25.840 --> 10:28.120
I don't want to go home
for the summer either,

10:28.200 --> 10:30.960
so I want to talk to my mom about it.

10:31.040 --> 10:32.760
I think getting a summer internship

10:32.840 --> 10:34.600
is better than staying at home.

10:34.680 --> 10:36.480
Agreed. Totally agreed.

10:38.720 --> 10:39.560
Yu Xin.

10:40.080 --> 10:41.000
What do I need

10:41.080 --> 10:42.920
to include in my resume?

10:43.000 --> 10:44.040
It's important

10:44.600 --> 10:45.880
to highlight your specialty.

10:46.440 --> 10:47.320
Let me take notes.

10:48.520 --> 10:49.720
And don't forget.

10:49.800 --> 10:51.880
Aren't you good at system maintenance?

10:51.960 --> 10:53.680
Put your system maintenance portfolio on--

10:53.760 --> 10:55.360
- The first page.
- Yes.

10:55.440 --> 10:57.960
- The most visible section.
- Yes. And then…

10:59.920 --> 11:00.760
SANG ZHI

11:00.840 --> 11:01.800
Sang Yan.

11:09.200 --> 11:11.240
What do you want?

11:11.320 --> 11:15.800
SILLY DOG

11:15.880 --> 11:20.000
SILLY DOG

11:21.280 --> 11:23.080
I don't want to go home for the summer.

11:24.360 --> 11:26.760
I plan to get an internship here

11:26.840 --> 11:28.920
to enrich my university life.

11:29.560 --> 11:32.080
I don't want to waste my youth.

11:32.160 --> 11:33.400
While I'm still young,

11:33.480 --> 11:35.360
I want to try everything I can.

11:35.440 --> 11:36.320
So

11:36.880 --> 11:39.680
can you help me talk
to Mom and Dad about this?

11:41.840 --> 11:43.000
If Mom still pressures you

11:43.080 --> 11:45.040
to get married during Chinese New Year,

11:45.120 --> 11:46.960
I'll speak up for you.

11:49.680 --> 11:53.120
SANG ZHI

12:03.200 --> 12:04.520
Let me ask you.

12:04.600 --> 12:06.800
Is your postgraduate boyfriend going home?

12:08.360 --> 12:10.160
Listen, you're coming home for the summer.

12:11.360 --> 12:12.440
Listen to yourself.

12:12.520 --> 12:14.360
I'm embarrassed for you
even through the screen.

12:27.600 --> 12:30.600
SILLY DOG

12:30.680 --> 12:32.280
Don't call me. I'm busy right now.

12:45.640 --> 12:46.560
Sang Yan.

12:47.120 --> 12:48.920
I told you.

12:49.000 --> 12:51.280
I'm staying here for an internship,

12:51.360 --> 12:52.680
for work.

12:52.760 --> 12:54.440
It's not for dating.

12:55.320 --> 12:56.160
Besides,

12:57.400 --> 12:58.840
the person I'm interested in

12:58.920 --> 13:00.760
is older than you,

13:00.840 --> 13:03.440
but not older than Dad.

13:03.520 --> 13:05.760
Don't be so petty.

13:05.840 --> 13:08.600
Just because you didn't date in college

13:08.680 --> 13:10.080
and can't find a girlfriend now,

13:10.160 --> 13:11.400
you can't be jealous of me.

13:11.480 --> 13:13.560
You need to be more magnanimous.

13:16.040 --> 13:17.320
Don't get it wrong.

13:17.400 --> 13:19.040
I'm not jealous at all.

13:19.120 --> 13:22.680
I have a girlfriend.

13:25.920 --> 13:27.080
Also, let me tell you.

13:27.160 --> 13:29.360
Don't become stupid after falling in love.

13:29.440 --> 13:31.400
When you met your online friend
during high school,

13:31.480 --> 13:33.000
you were only young and rebellious.

13:34.440 --> 13:35.880
You have to come home for the summer.

13:35.960 --> 13:36.800
Listen.

13:37.720 --> 13:39.720
I dare you to not come back.

13:39.800 --> 13:41.960
I'll fly there and drag you home myself.

13:48.280 --> 13:49.120
Who…

13:50.320 --> 13:52.680
Who would believe
that you have a girlfriend?

13:53.400 --> 13:54.680
You are just lying to me.

13:55.440 --> 13:56.720
And besides…

13:57.240 --> 13:59.120
Besides, I am staying

13:59.600 --> 14:01.560
to work at an internship.

14:01.640 --> 14:03.120
If you don't agree,

14:03.200 --> 14:04.800
I will tell Mom.

14:07.320 --> 14:08.640
You are so irritating!

14:13.000 --> 14:14.600
Why didn't you invite Chen Qiang?

14:15.200 --> 14:16.800
The professor told him to go

14:16.880 --> 14:18.360
and retake the test.

14:19.280 --> 14:21.520
- Let's have dumplings again later.
- Noodles.

14:21.600 --> 14:23.200
- Dumplings!
- Let's have noodles again.

14:23.280 --> 14:24.560
- Just once.
- It's really good.

14:24.640 --> 14:25.840
Give me a minute.

14:25.920 --> 14:26.920
Just a minute.

14:28.040 --> 14:29.040
Where are you going?

14:29.120 --> 14:29.960
What are you doing?

14:36.480 --> 14:37.400
Jiang Ming.

14:37.960 --> 14:38.800
Hi, Wangwang.

14:39.920 --> 14:41.080
This is for you.

14:41.160 --> 14:42.680
My mom said this works well

14:42.760 --> 14:43.960
for bruises and sprains.

14:45.680 --> 14:46.520
Thank you.

14:47.160 --> 14:49.120
What is going on?

14:50.760 --> 14:53.480
- At the basketball court yesterday,
- What is she doing?

14:53.560 --> 14:55.200
you asked about Sangsang's brother.

14:56.320 --> 14:57.240
It's okay.

14:57.720 --> 14:59.280
Sang Zhi has found someone she likes.

14:59.360 --> 15:00.400
I should be happy for her.

15:01.960 --> 15:03.640
- Sang Zhi?
- I'm glad you're okay.

15:05.000 --> 15:06.520
They are talking and smiling.

15:08.240 --> 15:09.640
Thank you for the ointment.

15:09.720 --> 15:11.880
I'll return it when I'm done with it.

15:11.960 --> 15:12.960
It's okay.

15:13.040 --> 15:14.240
I'm leaving now.

15:14.320 --> 15:15.200
Okay.

15:16.040 --> 15:17.520
- Bye.
- Bye.

15:20.200 --> 15:21.560
- What was that?
- What's going on?

15:21.640 --> 15:23.040
- What's up?
- What's the situation?

15:23.800 --> 15:24.640
I knew it!

15:24.720 --> 15:26.080
I could tell that day at the court.

15:26.160 --> 15:27.640
You rushed to him when he was injured!

15:28.440 --> 15:29.840
You are quite something.

15:29.920 --> 15:31.320
So what's your plan?

15:31.400 --> 15:32.680
Well…

15:33.240 --> 15:34.880
What? Go after him if you like him.

15:34.960 --> 15:37.200
- Don't hesitate.
- Yu Xin, you're catching on.

15:37.280 --> 15:38.280
Get lost.

15:39.240 --> 15:41.440
The video-editing course this semester

15:41.520 --> 15:43.040
wants us to conduct an interview.

15:43.120 --> 15:45.320
I was thinking of interviewing Jiang Ming.

15:45.920 --> 15:47.160
Do you think

15:47.640 --> 15:49.360
he will agree to it?

15:49.920 --> 15:51.600
He's right there. Just ask him yourself.

15:51.680 --> 15:52.960
- Right.
- It's a great opportunity.

15:53.040 --> 15:55.400
The two of you
can spend some time together.

15:55.480 --> 15:56.320
Good for you.

15:56.400 --> 15:57.280
You've got some moves.

15:57.360 --> 15:58.760
- Impressive.
- You are good at this.

15:58.840 --> 16:00.360
Stop teasing me.

16:00.440 --> 16:04.000
THE DREAM GAMES

16:42.120 --> 16:43.360
Are you still in class?

16:48.960 --> 16:50.240
Let's get beef noodles later.

16:50.320 --> 16:51.200
Sure.

16:52.880 --> 16:53.720
SANG ZHI

16:53.800 --> 16:55.280
Are you off work?

16:57.800 --> 16:58.640
Yes.

16:58.720 --> 16:59.560
DUAN JIAXU

16:59.640 --> 17:01.240
Do you not have classes this evening?

17:01.320 --> 17:02.640
DUAN JIAXU

17:06.520 --> 17:07.839
I have plans tonight.

17:13.119 --> 17:14.160
What plans?

17:42.040 --> 17:43.520
You said you have plans tonight.

17:43.600 --> 17:44.560
I do.

17:44.640 --> 17:46.240
I have to celebrate someone's birthday.

17:49.800 --> 17:51.520
Happy birthday.

17:54.320 --> 17:56.440
I forgot that it's my birthday.

17:57.440 --> 17:58.360
I understand.

17:58.440 --> 18:00.680
Old people don't like
celebrating their birthdays.

18:00.760 --> 18:01.960
My dad is the same.

18:02.480 --> 18:04.840
Yes, I'm getting old.

18:06.000 --> 18:06.920
That's why

18:08.200 --> 18:11.280
I hope you can help me get married
before I turn 27.

18:14.080 --> 18:15.440
When you are 27,

18:16.040 --> 18:17.240
I won't have graduated yet.

18:17.320 --> 18:18.920
So who are you going to marry?

18:19.480 --> 18:20.720
From the sound of that,

18:21.560 --> 18:23.000
I don't think you refused.

18:24.000 --> 18:25.280
So I'll take that as a yes.

18:26.000 --> 18:27.280
You're so shameless.

18:27.360 --> 18:28.360
Of course.

18:28.440 --> 18:29.880
I'm pursuing a young girl

18:29.960 --> 18:32.040
and someone as difficult as you at that.

18:32.120 --> 18:33.400
Of course I have to be shameless.

18:34.800 --> 18:36.160
So you think I'm difficult.

18:56.560 --> 18:57.400
By the way,

18:58.120 --> 18:59.960
did my brother, Qian Fei, and the others

19:00.040 --> 19:01.520
wish you a happy birthday?

19:01.600 --> 19:03.720
They don't even remember
their own birthdays.

19:03.800 --> 19:04.920
Why would they remember mine?

19:06.280 --> 19:07.360
So they haven't?

19:08.480 --> 19:10.280
What about your colleagues?

19:10.880 --> 19:12.560
Did they celebrate your birthday today?

19:14.640 --> 19:16.520
They are all so busy.

19:16.600 --> 19:18.480
They don't have time for these things.

19:29.600 --> 19:32.480
Do you know what day it is today?

19:32.560 --> 19:33.400
SILLY DOG

19:37.320 --> 19:38.160
SENIOR

19:38.240 --> 19:39.720
Remember to send me the design.

19:44.000 --> 19:45.480
Who are you texting?

19:47.440 --> 19:48.680
A senior classmate.

19:50.320 --> 19:51.400
A senior classmate?

19:51.960 --> 19:52.800
What does he want?

19:54.160 --> 19:55.680
It's about a school event.

19:58.560 --> 19:59.760
Is he handsome?

20:01.840 --> 20:03.160
Morally upright?

20:03.800 --> 20:05.520
Is he a head taller than you?

20:07.120 --> 20:08.960
He has a girlfriend.

20:10.360 --> 20:11.600
I'm just asking.

20:16.760 --> 20:18.520
SANG YAN

20:21.720 --> 20:24.360
Why is my brother suddenly calling you?

20:24.440 --> 20:25.360
That's strange.

20:26.520 --> 20:28.840
You're right. I'll reject the call then.

20:28.920 --> 20:30.960
Answer it.

20:35.120 --> 20:36.000
Hi.

20:36.560 --> 20:38.080
Hello, Duan Jiaxu.

20:38.680 --> 20:41.160
I just remembered
that it's your birthday today.

20:42.800 --> 20:44.080
Yes. So?

20:44.160 --> 20:45.960
Congratulations, buddy.

20:46.040 --> 20:48.320
Even at your age,
you still don't have a girlfriend.

20:49.000 --> 20:50.680
By the way, let me ask you a question.

20:50.760 --> 20:51.880
I'm hanging up.

20:51.960 --> 20:53.360
No, hang on.

20:53.440 --> 20:55.240
Did my sister give you the gift?

21:00.040 --> 21:01.320
Yes.

21:01.400 --> 21:02.840
That one is from me.

21:05.560 --> 21:07.000
That's all.

21:07.080 --> 21:08.960
I'm just calling to wish you
a happy birthday.

21:09.440 --> 21:11.320
By the way, let me ask you something.

21:11.880 --> 21:13.560
Have you met my sister's boyfriend?

21:20.200 --> 21:21.240
Boyfriend?

21:22.840 --> 21:25.240
I told you. It's a postgraduate student.

21:29.000 --> 21:30.200
I remember now.

21:30.280 --> 21:31.640
I think I've met him.

21:32.120 --> 21:33.800
What kind of guy is he?

21:33.880 --> 21:35.360
The little demon is quite infatuated.

21:35.440 --> 21:37.440
She plans on staying in Yihe
and not coming home.

21:37.520 --> 21:39.400
- I don't know what charm he has---
- Sang Yan.

21:42.440 --> 21:44.680
Was that my sister?

21:45.240 --> 21:46.720
Are you two together?

21:50.640 --> 21:51.840
Yes.

21:51.920 --> 21:53.080
You…

21:53.160 --> 21:55.000
You've wished him a happy birthday,

21:55.080 --> 21:56.360
so you can hang up now.

21:57.120 --> 21:59.080
Don't tell me you two--

21:59.160 --> 22:00.360
No.

22:00.440 --> 22:01.840
No.

22:02.440 --> 22:03.400
Don't overthink it.

22:03.880 --> 22:05.960
You said no before I even finished.

22:06.040 --> 22:07.400
Why are you so worked up?

22:07.480 --> 22:09.120
I know what you were going to say.

22:09.200 --> 22:10.360
That's enough.

22:10.440 --> 22:11.360
You can hang up now.

22:11.440 --> 22:12.880
Are you two having dinner together?

22:14.120 --> 22:15.360
Yes.

22:15.440 --> 22:18.240
I can't be a heartless friend like you.

22:18.920 --> 22:19.760
Also,

22:20.280 --> 22:21.960
why did you say

22:22.040 --> 22:23.520
the gift was from you?

22:23.600 --> 22:26.120
I bought the gift for him.

22:27.760 --> 22:29.960
Isn't it a bit schmaltzy for a grown man

22:30.040 --> 22:31.440
to celebrate his birthday?

22:31.520 --> 22:32.720
Little demon,

22:32.800 --> 22:34.520
don't stay out too late.

22:34.600 --> 22:35.600
I'm hanging up now.

22:35.680 --> 22:36.800
Just hang up.

22:37.440 --> 22:38.560
Good night, buddy.

22:38.640 --> 22:39.480
Have an early night.

22:43.920 --> 22:46.040
Boyfriend?

22:47.800 --> 22:49.320
What boyfriend?

22:53.120 --> 22:54.680
I told him

22:56.360 --> 22:58.120
that I'm about to start dating,

22:58.200 --> 22:59.520
not that I'm already dating.

22:59.600 --> 23:00.960
He misunderstood.

23:02.160 --> 23:03.560
A postgraduate student?

23:05.080 --> 23:06.680
Is it too late for me to apply?

23:08.360 --> 23:10.160
How else will we explain it to Sang Yan?

23:11.400 --> 23:12.600
Maybe we can tell him

23:13.520 --> 23:16.040
that you broke up
with that postgraduate boyfriend

23:16.120 --> 23:17.480
and got together with me.

23:17.560 --> 23:19.440
That might work.

23:19.520 --> 23:21.520
That definitely won't work.

23:24.440 --> 23:27.160
When did I get together with you?

23:27.240 --> 23:28.280
That's so weird.

23:29.760 --> 23:31.680
You've already told your brother.

23:32.240 --> 23:33.760
And you still won't admit to liking me?

23:37.160 --> 23:40.360
Did you already know?

23:42.200 --> 23:43.120
Know what?

23:53.600 --> 23:55.280
All right, jokes aside,

23:55.360 --> 23:56.800
let me ask you something.

23:58.760 --> 24:00.240
Go on.

24:00.320 --> 24:02.200
Do you really have no feelings for me?

24:11.600 --> 24:13.080
Maybe just a little bit.

24:17.080 --> 24:18.160
Okay.

24:22.640 --> 24:24.080
Why aren't you surprised?

24:30.960 --> 24:33.000
Don't you find it strange

24:33.080 --> 24:35.640
that I have feelings for you,

24:35.720 --> 24:37.080
but won't agree to be with you

24:37.160 --> 24:38.640
and am making you pursue me?

24:39.880 --> 24:41.680
You said it's only a little bit.

24:41.760 --> 24:43.000
It's probably not strong enough

24:43.080 --> 24:44.320
for you to want to date me.

24:46.120 --> 24:47.720
What if I never agree

24:47.800 --> 24:49.120
to be with you?

24:49.200 --> 24:51.440
Then I will pursue you every day.

24:52.600 --> 24:53.680
After all,

24:54.280 --> 24:56.960
this might be the only relationship
you'll have in your whole life.

25:00.000 --> 25:02.600
So whatever other young girls have,

25:02.680 --> 25:03.960
Zhizhi

25:04.680 --> 25:06.080
has to have it too.

25:29.080 --> 25:30.840
Ms. Sang, everything is ready for you.

25:30.920 --> 25:31.840
This way, please.

25:31.920 --> 25:34.760
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

25:34.840 --> 25:37.040
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

25:37.120 --> 25:38.000
What is this?

25:38.080 --> 25:40.360
- Happy birthday to you
- What is this?

25:40.840 --> 25:43.680
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

25:43.760 --> 25:44.920
Thank you.

25:51.160 --> 25:53.720
HAPPY BIRTHDAY

26:03.160 --> 26:04.880
They are getting off work soon.

26:04.960 --> 26:06.400
From here on, it's all on me.

26:08.360 --> 26:09.680
Wait for me here.

26:09.760 --> 26:12.200
I'll prepare a mysterious feast

26:12.280 --> 26:13.600
for you.

26:14.160 --> 26:15.160
I will come with you.

26:15.640 --> 26:17.000
No need.

26:17.080 --> 26:18.160
I'll go by myself.

26:18.240 --> 26:19.520
It's very mysterious.

26:19.600 --> 26:20.640
I'm making it myself.

26:27.440 --> 26:31.720
HAPPY BIRTHDAY

26:37.440 --> 26:38.440
Thank you for your help.

26:38.520 --> 26:39.400
Go home now.

26:39.960 --> 26:40.880
Good luck.

26:49.800 --> 26:54.480
MOM'S HANDMADE
LONGEVITY NOODLES RECIPE

27:12.040 --> 27:13.640
Mushroom.

27:14.520 --> 27:15.680
Mushroom.

27:17.000 --> 27:18.840
Cut twice.

27:19.480 --> 27:21.920
Use a garnishing knife.

27:22.520 --> 27:24.680
And then…

27:39.200 --> 27:41.160
So is this my birthday feast?

27:41.240 --> 27:42.400
You…

27:42.480 --> 27:43.800
Why did you come inside?

27:43.880 --> 27:45.280
Wait outside.

27:45.360 --> 27:47.080
I'll be done soon. Very soon.

27:47.160 --> 27:48.680
Are you sure you can do it by yourself?

27:49.200 --> 27:50.320
It's very simple.

27:51.120 --> 27:53.200
- You don't need any help?
- I really don't. Go out.

27:53.840 --> 27:54.720
Good luck.

27:54.800 --> 27:56.000
It's very easy.

27:56.080 --> 27:57.720
It's fine. Don't worry about me.

28:09.600 --> 28:11.240
Add these in.

28:19.120 --> 28:20.000
Add the noodles.

28:54.560 --> 28:55.520
How is it?

28:56.280 --> 28:58.080
HAPPY BIRTHDAY

28:59.360 --> 29:00.280
Let me try it.

29:01.320 --> 29:02.560
Don't try it.

29:02.640 --> 29:03.680
You can

29:03.760 --> 29:05.840
just take a photo for a memento.

29:05.920 --> 29:08.920
I haven't tasted it,

29:09.000 --> 29:09.960
so I think…

29:42.680 --> 29:43.840
Is it edible?

29:45.040 --> 29:46.240
It's good.

29:48.720 --> 29:49.800
It's good?

29:49.880 --> 29:50.760
Yes.

29:52.280 --> 29:53.160
No way.

29:53.240 --> 29:55.000
Let me try it.

29:55.080 --> 29:56.200
- No.
- Why?

29:56.280 --> 29:57.880
You made this for me.

29:58.840 --> 30:00.240
I have to finish it all by myself.

30:01.000 --> 30:02.440
It must taste awful.

30:03.200 --> 30:04.240
It's really good.

30:04.320 --> 30:05.480
Stop eating.

30:23.400 --> 30:26.160
This year, you can make three wishes.

30:26.800 --> 30:28.800
Two wishes can be spoken out.

30:28.880 --> 30:30.440
Keep the last one to yourself.

30:38.280 --> 30:40.440
Wishes won't come true
if there are too many.

30:41.800 --> 30:43.040
I only have one wish.

30:45.040 --> 30:46.120
That's fine too.

31:13.560 --> 31:15.080
Happy birthday.

31:15.720 --> 31:17.440
- Thank you.
- What did you wish for?

31:20.040 --> 31:20.960
You know what it is.

32:00.520 --> 32:01.480
Well…

32:03.440 --> 32:05.800
Your wish is too easy to fulfill.

32:09.120 --> 32:10.720
The answer is yes.

32:19.040 --> 32:20.200
Are you saying

32:21.680 --> 32:23.560
that you will be my girlfriend?

32:25.720 --> 32:27.320
That's because I want

32:29.080 --> 32:30.600
to be by your side

32:32.000 --> 32:33.680
for all your future birthdays.

32:38.000 --> 32:39.000
Can I?

32:40.320 --> 32:41.360
Of course you can.

32:47.800 --> 32:49.120
Then

32:50.400 --> 32:51.760
I will cut the cake for you.

33:11.000 --> 33:12.800
The birthday boy eats first.

33:21.000 --> 33:21.920
What?

34:10.159 --> 34:11.080
I

34:12.199 --> 34:14.080
don't really know how to do this.

34:17.880 --> 34:19.560
You always call me old.

34:20.520 --> 34:22.560
It's quite embarrassing

34:24.000 --> 34:25.320
to admit this myself.

34:27.080 --> 34:29.080
This is also my first relationship.

34:31.239 --> 34:32.360
And it is also

34:34.400 --> 34:36.000
my first time liking someone so much.

34:39.840 --> 34:41.000
So

34:43.120 --> 34:45.000
don't even think about dumping me.

35:20.080 --> 35:21.840
Why do you keep staring at me?

35:26.200 --> 35:27.600
I just didn't expect you

35:28.480 --> 35:30.240
to say yes so soon.

35:31.160 --> 35:33.080
I feel that today is very special.

35:34.040 --> 35:35.040
How so?

35:39.360 --> 35:41.880
Firstly, this is your first birthday

35:41.960 --> 35:44.000
that I've celebrated with you.

35:45.840 --> 35:48.960
And it's also our first day together.

35:51.600 --> 35:52.840
From now on,

35:54.720 --> 35:56.720
I'll always be by your side.

36:11.280 --> 36:12.640
By the way,

36:13.800 --> 36:15.520
there are some things

36:15.600 --> 36:17.320
I feel I should let you know.

36:19.600 --> 36:21.400
I don't think I've told you

36:21.960 --> 36:23.800
about my family situation.

36:24.680 --> 36:25.880
The thing is,

36:26.680 --> 36:28.720
my mom has passed away.

36:29.760 --> 36:30.840
And my dad

36:31.440 --> 36:32.440
is in a coma.

36:33.440 --> 36:35.800
He killed someone while drunk driving.

36:36.640 --> 36:38.720
But I've paid off the compensation.

36:40.480 --> 36:41.640
Right now,

36:42.440 --> 36:43.440
I don't

36:44.000 --> 36:45.080
own a house,

36:45.160 --> 36:46.440
but I have a car.

36:46.520 --> 36:48.000
I also have some savings.

36:54.000 --> 36:55.040
I'm sorry

36:56.840 --> 36:58.880
to bring this up out of the blue.

36:59.960 --> 37:01.200
Please don't feel uncomfortable.

37:01.280 --> 37:03.360
I'm not uncomfortable.

37:04.560 --> 37:07.000
I'm just worried
that talking about these things

37:08.600 --> 37:10.040
might make you sad.

37:11.760 --> 37:13.280
Why would I feel sad?

37:16.400 --> 37:17.680
But

37:19.640 --> 37:21.920
I admit that I might be a bit nervous.

37:24.680 --> 37:25.800
Why?

37:31.880 --> 37:33.800
I'm worried that you will mind.

37:36.560 --> 37:37.920
I don't mind.

38:11.680 --> 38:13.560
Sang Zhi, is there a power outage?

38:13.640 --> 38:14.760
I think so.

38:14.840 --> 38:15.680
Okay.

38:19.600 --> 38:20.440
Hello.

38:20.520 --> 38:22.960
Girlfriend, are you free later?

38:23.040 --> 38:24.120
Let's have lunch together.

38:25.080 --> 38:26.920
I'm going to the library to study.

38:27.000 --> 38:28.440
How about another day?

38:28.520 --> 38:29.680
The library?

38:30.320 --> 38:31.400
Can't you keep me company?

38:32.160 --> 38:33.040
Another day.

38:33.120 --> 38:34.040
All right then.

38:34.120 --> 38:35.120
Bye.

38:50.560 --> 38:51.680
What are you doing here?

38:52.280 --> 38:54.040
The power is out.
There's nowhere to study.

38:54.120 --> 38:55.200
Why didn't you tell me?

38:56.080 --> 38:58.040
I was just about to go to the library.

38:58.120 --> 38:59.720
I know which library you mean.

38:59.800 --> 39:01.240
It's the one nearby.

39:01.320 --> 39:02.520
There is very limited seating.

39:02.600 --> 39:04.440
All seats will have been taken by now.

39:05.680 --> 39:06.600
Then…

39:07.720 --> 39:09.840
- There is a café up ahead.
- Come to my place.

39:12.000 --> 39:13.080
Your place?

39:14.760 --> 39:15.720
To study.

39:21.080 --> 39:22.440
You haven't eaten, right?

39:22.520 --> 39:23.440
Perfect.

39:23.520 --> 39:25.160
I'll make something tasty for you later.

39:25.240 --> 39:26.560
You can cook too?

39:27.960 --> 39:29.240
I have a lot of skills.

39:29.920 --> 39:30.840
Such as?

39:32.000 --> 39:33.200
Such as…

39:51.280 --> 39:52.560
Change into slippers.

39:56.600 --> 39:58.640
You can study in my room later.

39:59.400 --> 40:00.480
There's a desk inside.

40:02.360 --> 40:03.240
I…

40:04.040 --> 40:07.560
I can just study here.

40:07.640 --> 40:09.560
I don't need to go to your room.

40:09.640 --> 40:11.600
I'll be cooking here later.

40:11.680 --> 40:13.400
Won't I disturb your studying?

40:17.280 --> 40:18.440
What are you thinking?

40:23.280 --> 40:25.120
I've already tidied up the desk for you.

40:30.200 --> 40:31.880
Study well.

40:32.720 --> 40:36.560
Jiaxu, what will you be doing

40:36.640 --> 40:37.720
while I study?

40:39.040 --> 40:40.120
I will

40:40.200 --> 40:41.400
just be sitting here.

40:43.560 --> 40:44.720
You'll just be sitting here?

40:45.360 --> 40:47.800
I want to look at you more.

41:19.120 --> 41:23.880
LUOKA BAKING

41:23.960 --> 41:25.040
Welcome.

41:25.120 --> 41:26.760
- Hi.
- Hi.

41:26.840 --> 41:28.120
Excuse me.

41:28.200 --> 41:29.760
Do you make personalized cakes?

41:29.840 --> 41:31.080
Yes, we do.

41:31.800 --> 41:32.960
I have a picture.

41:33.720 --> 41:35.080
Can you make something like this?

41:35.720 --> 41:36.560
Yes, we can.

41:36.640 --> 41:38.400
When would you like to have it?

41:38.920 --> 41:40.360
Is next Monday okay?

41:41.240 --> 41:42.840
Yes. Let me take it down.

41:48.800 --> 41:50.000
Miss, what is your surname?

41:50.080 --> 41:50.920
Sang.

41:54.840 --> 41:56.520
An eight-inch cake.

41:56.600 --> 41:57.720
Miss, your phone is ringing.

41:58.280 --> 41:59.680
Have you taken a photo?

41:59.760 --> 42:01.080
Yes. Go ahead.

42:03.960 --> 42:04.880
Hello, Mom.

42:04.960 --> 42:06.120
Hi, Zhizhi.

42:07.400 --> 42:09.000
I was outside just now.

42:09.080 --> 42:10.360
I just got home.

42:10.440 --> 42:13.600
Did you say something
about the recipe for longevity noodles?

42:13.680 --> 42:15.280
Is it someone's birthday?

42:16.080 --> 42:17.560
It's Jiaxu's birthday.

42:18.600 --> 42:19.720
So it's Xiaoduan.

42:21.720 --> 42:24.360
I'm studying in Yihe

42:24.440 --> 42:26.920
and Jiaxu has been taking care of me.

42:27.680 --> 42:29.440
He's all alone here.

42:29.520 --> 42:32.040
So I thought

42:32.560 --> 42:35.640
I would make longevity noodles for him.

42:35.720 --> 42:36.640
But

42:36.720 --> 42:39.240
I'm sure you make the most delicious one.

42:40.680 --> 42:42.600
You're becoming more considerate.

42:43.800 --> 42:46.200
Okay, I'll write out the recipe
for longevity noodles

42:46.280 --> 42:47.320
and send it to you later.

42:47.400 --> 42:48.560
Okay.

42:52.680 --> 42:53.520
Bye.

42:56.040 --> 42:57.520
Miss, take a look.

42:57.600 --> 42:59.120
It will be an eight-inch cake

42:59.200 --> 43:00.600
to be picked up next Monday.

43:00.680 --> 43:02.040
Will you be picking it up yourself?

43:02.120 --> 43:03.440
- Yes.
- Okay.

43:03.520 --> 43:04.920
It's all set.

43:05.000 --> 43:05.840
Thank you.
